%91%D8%AF%D9%8E"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to wreathe, to wind, to twist"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to ladle out, to collect"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to imitate, to ape, to represent on the stage","examples":[{"text":"قَرَّرَ أَنْ يُقَلَّدَ أُسْلُوبَ الرَّاقِصِ الشَّهِيرِ.","english":"He decided to imitate the style of the famous dancer."}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to wind round"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to adorn with a necklace; to put on a necktie"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to gird with a sword"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to invest, to make (someone) a prince, to give (someone) full power"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to hand down old sayings, truths, traditions, etc."}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n36120","headword_ar":"قَلَدَ","root":"qld","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qalodN","text_ar":"قَلْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", L.)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He twisted, wound,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wreathed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"a thing (or anything, L,) upon ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ElY","text_ar":"على"},{"kind":"text","text":") another thing; (L, K;) as a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qulob","text_ar":"قُلْب"},{"kind":"text","text":"(the ornament so called) upon another"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qulob","text_ar":"قُلْب"},{"kind":"text","text":". (L.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,] aor. and inf. n. as above (S, L)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He twisted"},{"kind":"text","text":"a rope. (S, L, K.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qulida Haboluhu","text_ar":"قُلِدَ حَبْلُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His rope was twisted:"},{"kind":"text","text":"said of an old man who has become weak in judgment by reason of age, and whose opinion is not regarded. (IAar, L.) ―         -b3-  [Hence, also,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made"},{"kind":"text","text":"a piece of iron"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"slender, and twisted, wound,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wreathed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"it (K) upon a similar piece, (TA,) or upon another thing. (K.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaladatohu AlHum~aY","text_ar":"قَلَدَتْهُ الحُمَّى"},{"kind":"text","text":", (aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qalodN","text_ar":"قَلْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", L,) (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The fever seized him every day."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K.) See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qilodN","text_ar":"قِلْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qalada","text_ar":"قَلَدَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qalodN","text_ar":"قَلْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", L,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He irrigated"},{"kind":"text","text":"growing corn. (L, K.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qalada","text_ar":"قَلَدَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qalodN","text_ar":"قَلْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", L,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He collected"},{"kind":"text","text":"water in a tank or cistern, (L, K,) and milk in a skin, (IAar, L, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ladling"},{"kind":"text","text":"each"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"out with a bowl,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and pouring it into the tank or the skin, (AZ,) and clarified butter in a skin, (L,) and beverage, or wine, in his belly. (L, K.) See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qrd","text_ar":"قرد"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qalada mina","text_ar":"قَلَدَ مِنَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al$~araAb fiY jawofihi","text_ar":"الشَّرَاب فِى جَوْفِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He drank of the beverage,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wine."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IKtt.)"}],"source_refs":["S","L","K","TA","IAar","AZ"]},{"entry_id":"n36124","headword_ar":"قَلْدٌ","root":"qld","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maqoluwdN","text_ar":"مَقْلُودٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n36125","headword_ar":"قِلْدٌ","root":"qld","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A single strand,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"twist,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a rope; (AHn, ISd;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the like"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a bracelet: (see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qulobN","text_ar":"قُلْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aqolaAdN","text_ar":"اَقْلَادٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quluwdN","text_ar":"قُلُودٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (AHn, ISd.) See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maqoluwdN","text_ar":"مَقْلُودٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b2-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"day on which a fever comes:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K:) or,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"on which a regular intermittent fever returns, seldom failing to do so at a particular time:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L:) or,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"on which a quartan fever comes:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L, K: *) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aqolaAdN","text_ar":"اَقْلَادٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (L.) ―         -b3-  Hence, (S, L.) The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"caravans from Mekkeh to Juddeh."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L, K.) ―         -b4-  Accord. to As, A man"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"attacked by a quartan fever on the day of its attack."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Irrigation"},{"kind":"text","text":"of growing corn: (Az, L:) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaliydN","text_ar":"قَلِيدٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (L.) ―         -b2-  [And]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qilodN","text_ar":"قِلْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"day of irrigation."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aqaAma","text_ar":"اَقَامَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qilodahu mina AlmaA='i","text_ar":"قِلْدَهُ مِنَ المَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He performed the work of irrigating his land on the day appointed for his doing so."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, from a trad.) ―         -b3-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Irrigation by rain every week."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saqatonaA Als~amaA='u qilodFA fiY kul~i","text_ar":"سَقَتْنَا السَّمَا=ءُ قِلْدًا فِى كُلِّ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^usobuwEK","text_ar":"اُسْبُوعٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The heaven rained upon us at a particular time every week:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L:) from the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qilod","text_ar":"قِلْد"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a fever. (L.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saqaY A_ibilahu qilodFA","text_ar":"سَقَى اـِبِلَهُ قِلْدًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He watered his camels every day at noon."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Fr, L.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kayofa qilodu naxoli","text_ar":"كَيْفَ قِلْدُ نَخْلِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baniY fulaAnK","text_ar":"بَنِى فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"How is the watering of the palm-trees of the sons of such a one?"},{"kind":"text","text":"] a question to which one may answer, They are watered (lit. they drink) once in every ten [nights]. (L.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A portion of water:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K:) [pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aqolaAdN","text_ar":"اَقْلَادٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", occurring in the A.]: and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qilodapN","text_ar":"قِلْدَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a draught"},{"kind":"text","text":"of water. (A.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEoTayotuhu qiloda A^amoriY","text_ar":"اَعْطَيْتُهُ قِلْدَ اَمْرِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I committed to him"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the management of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"my affair."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, K.)"}],"source_refs":["L","K","Az","S"]}]}}